After much messing around, I have discovered the gamepads' various buttons.
If you have a controller that isn't listed here, please test all of the inputs and write them here.

PS4 (Wireless Controller)
Button 0: Square
Button 1: X
Button 2: O
Button 3: Triangle
Button 4: L1
Button 5: R1
Button 6: L2
Button 7: R2
Button 8: Share
Button 9: Options
Button 10: LStick Press
Button 11: RStick Press
Button 12: PS Button
Button 13: Trackpad Press
Hat Switch: Dpad (.25 up, .5 right, .75 down, 1 left)
X Axis: LStick L/R
X Rotation: L2 Intensity
Y Axis: LStick U/D
Y Rotation: R2 Intensity
Z Axis: RStick L/R
Z Rotation: RStick U/D

Xbox (Controller (XBOX 360 For Windows))
Button 0: A
Button 1: B
Button 2: X
Button 3: Y
Button 4: LB
Button 5: RB
Button 6: Back
Button 7: Start
Button 8: LStick Press
Button 9: RStick Press
Hat Switch: Dpad (.25 up, .5 right, .75 down, 1 left)
X Axis: LStick L/R
X Rotation: RStick L/R
Y Axis: LStick U/D
Y Rotation: RStick U/D
Z Axis: LT Intensity - RT Intensity